        "description": "#### `GET /status` — Check API Status\n\nVerifies the API is online and operational.\n\n``` http\nGET {{baseUrl}}/status\n\n ```\n\n**Response:**\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"status\": \"OK\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n**Tests:**\n\n- Asserts the response status code is `200 OK`."
